<img src="http://68.media.tumblr.com/8d1da9090874f50ef0edb7990c7ac7cb/tumblr_om16gtUHco1qz4jbro1_500.jpg"/><br/><br/><p>I took my clean, shiny bike out for a spin in this morning’s mud and rain, to see not only how the forks were behaving, but also how my new seatpost pack fared. The stitching on the old KTM bag was pulling through by the time I finished the Welsh Trail Centres trip. I looked at a couple of different makes and models, and have ended up going for the new Alpkit Big Papa. Seemed steady today, no wag to speak of; more once I’ve got a few miles on it.</p>